<refsect2>
<title><anchor id="b-init"/>b_init ()</title>
<programlisting>void        b_init                          (void);</programlisting>
<para>
This function initializes the BLib library. It calls <link linkend="g-type-init">g_type_init</link>()
for you, initializes the random number generator and registers some
transform functions needed for the deserialization routines.
</para>
<para>
It is safe to call this function multiple times but you should at
least call it once before you use any other BLib functions.</para>
<para>

